packets.name: Son Goku HairStyle
packets.author: piandex
packets.description:
My first release of a hairstyle series!

Are you DragonBall fans? Here is a good news, inspired by the super cool hairstyle of Son Goku from the DragonBall Manga Series, grab this chance to be the first to have the Legendary Haircut in CryptoVoxel! 

Always Look Good to Feel Good!
_piandex_
